description._content: Description: View of Diorios Forest from the hut, showing natural reproduction of Aleppo Pine - Pinus halepensis after War Felling on 1918 - 1920. Photo 1930, Elevation 750 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1918 Description: View of nursery and natural reproduction of Aleppo Pine - Pinus halepensis, after War Felling of 1918 - 1920. Diorios Forest, Elevation 750 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1918 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
